com.facebook.buck.android.support.exopackage

Interface ApplicationLike

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    DefaultApplicationLike

    public interface ApplicationLike
    This interface is used to delegate calls from main Application object. Implementations of this interface must have a one-argument constructor that takes an argument of type Application.
